INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (2, '“迈”出不一样的亲子游', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/qingmai3.jpeg', '<div><h2>序</h2></div><p>这次之所以再次选择&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" target=\"_blank\">清迈</a>&nbsp;，是因为看到BLIG王阿琬的微信文章《环球旅居第一站：遇见不一样的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15284.html\" target=\"_blank\">清迈</a>，我的私藏小众亲子玩法》（有兴趣的也可以用微信搜索一下），让我迈出了带娃旅行的第一步，组团“妈妈去哪儿”&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/21.png\">&nbsp;<br>第一次带娃，行程安排得十分轻松，住的是独栋民宿，4个娃玩得不亦乐乎。<br>时间：3月21日-3月25日<br>人均：共5000元左右（一大一小）<br>机票（1300多）+住宿（1100多）+救助营和骑马门票（1000左右）+ 吃吃吃+交通费（包车&amp;打车）<br>签证：落地签，其实就是塞50元人民币或200株在护照本里，就可以通过了。<br>中午到达，排队十分钟左右。<br>团队成员：<br>我（队长）：负责机票和住宿预定，线路规划和沟通的主力。我崽是最小的，4岁。<br>星星（摄影担当）：就是自拍脸占半屏的女人，哈哈！女儿花花，4岁2个月。<br>VICKY（美食担当）：要吃住家饭，就靠她了！女儿诺诺，4岁7个月。<br>婷：最大的优势呢？就是带了个小队长出行&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/21.png\">&nbsp;，焌哥哥，6岁。</p><div><h2>DAY 1 澳门-清迈</h2></div><p>航班时间：11：15（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10206.html\" target=\"_blank\">澳门</a>&nbsp;时间）——12：55（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10083.html\" target=\"_blank\">泰国</a>&nbsp;时间）<br>所有小朋友都是第一次坐飞机，看他们期待的背影，不知多年以后是否还记得曾经的红尘作伴？</p><div id=\"_j_photo_444398937\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444398937.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AF/5B/wKgEaVye4JOAfW5RABF57FOlejI37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424831.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>澳门国际机场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444398935\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444398935.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AF/58/wKgEaVye4JCAVX3jAAKQl0B4Orw78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424831.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>澳门国际机场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444398938\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444398938.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AF/5C/wKgEaVye4JSAShfTAASarCRd0Ag47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424831.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>澳门国际机场</a></div><p>第一站：民宿<br>一进门，所有人都很兴奋，跟网上图片完全一模一样，让小盆友们控制不了寄几（看最后的图）&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/5.png\">&nbsp;<br>旁边就是房东开的咖啡厅，性价比特高。吃饱喝足后，每个小盆友选了一间卧室，开始午睡&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/19.png\"></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444395997\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395997.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/02/wKgEaVye3jaAXRbCAAk97Ma4y0o94.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395996\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395996.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/00/wKgEaVye3jWAW77HAApfb1GkgN422.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395998\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395998.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/03/wKgEaVye3jeAK1ubAAgjhHkfXlM75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395991\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395991.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AA/FA/wKgEaVye3jKAOae2AAYeO7hf6_k32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395992\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395992.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AA/FB/wKgEaVye3jOAQ74HAAg2V1pofjQ04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395994\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395994.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AA/FE/wKgEaVye3jSAUT_LAAYtSuE5PC872.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395995\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395995.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/00/wKgEaVye3jWAc3zWAAaxIE5wTYg13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444396002\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444396002.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/08/wKgEaVye3jmAPzQ6AAV0Zo_bjWk29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444395999\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444395999.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/04/wKgEaVye3jeAYgnkAAeQhoA2vqY47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444396000\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444396000.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AB/05/wKgEaVye3jiAS2T0AAOCD0rJhqI55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>咖啡厅门口：JUMP&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/63.png\"></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444504970\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444504970.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/45/9E/wKgEaVyfNyWAbptXAAvS8LtCOUc15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444504971\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444504971.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/45/A1/wKgEaVyfNyaAY5xrAAm_k-NJ58g87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>第二站：塔佩门——喂鸽子<br>恒哥不知为啥，从小就害怕动物，最开始的时候，我想拍他的照片，结果一张都没拍到...<br>为什么？就因为他想喂鸽子，但又害怕，一直跟在我屁股后面&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/79.png\">&nbsp;<br>后来，又忽然之间，能与鸽子好好相处&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/80.png\">&nbsp;看，跟花花姐姐喂得多开心~~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_444504974\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444504974.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/45/A8/wKgEaVyfNymASLYRAAtzkxqG8rs11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424032.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>塔佩门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444504976\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/15284/scenery_12449006/444504976.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/45/B2/wKgEaVyfNy2AW2_CABPamyypTPY95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div>', '序这次之所以再次选择 ;清迈 ;，是因为看到BLIG王阿琬的微信文章《环球旅居第一站：遇见不一样的 ;清迈，我的私藏小众亲子玩法》（有兴趣的也可以用微信搜索一下），让我迈出了带娃旅行的第一步，组团“妈妈去哪儿” ; ;第一次带娃，行程安排得十分轻松，住的是...', '2019-05-03 00:00:00', 7, 3600, 1, '潘大美女', '2019-04-29 10:33:37', '2019-05-05 18:31:57', '清迈', '清迈', 2, 26, 1);
INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (3, '宏村+黄山，一场女汉纸的自虐之旅', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/huangshan1.jpeg', '<p>2019年04月13日，我向自己预约了这篇游记，当时我说：心心念念已久的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;之行终于成行了！<br>春节前就想着去一次&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;，后来因为时间问题，迟迟未能成行。2月底因一次工作的调整变动，心情低落到了谷底，再加上因为大笨猪的事情，持续的低落情绪让自己总想逃离&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;，哪怕是短暂的离开几天，于是旅行出游成了唯一的选择。也正因为如此，促成了这次的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;之旅。一行四个小伙伴，决定来一场三天两晚的背包自虐之旅。<br>提前在网上订好了高铁票及&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;的住宿，为了方便一些，包了一辆车，负责到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;高铁北站接至&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;、从&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;接送到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;景区换乘中心，最后到换乘中心接送至&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;高铁北站。<br>往返高铁票+&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;住宿+&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;山顶住宿+包车=1459元/人。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;山顶的住宿较贵，标间一般基本至少在八九百一晚，进入旺季后基本要涨至1200左右甚至更贵，且需要提前预定。</p><div><h2>行程概括</h2></div><p>Day1（4月19日）：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;北—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;<br>Day2（4月20日）：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;景区<br>Day3（4月21日）：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;北—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;<br>这次选择在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;山顶住一晚，所以背包徒步爬&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;成了唯一的选择。为了减轻负担，能不带的坚决不带，可有可无的，尽量不带。带上换洗衣服和简单的洗漱用品，所有行李就一个背包，当然那对钥匙扣依然会随身携带。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823361\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823361.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2D/F8/wKgEaVy_3ViALpY_AADD1o-Rpgs16.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div><h2>Day 1：出发，宏村我们来了</h2></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823373\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823373.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2D/FE/wKgEaVy_3VuAfEXUAABQjb7OUgg92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>由于只有三天时间，为了游玩时间的充裕，选择了最早的一班&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;的高铁，但&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;北至&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>北的火车票已售完，而多买一站到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10045.html\" target=\"_blank\">婺源</a>&nbsp;的车票还有，于是购买了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html\" target=\"_blank\">苏州</a>&nbsp;北到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10045.html\" target=\"_blank\">婺源</a>&nbsp;的高铁票，提前一站下车。<br>早上8点12的高铁票，8点多一点才赶到高铁北站，一路狂奔，安检、检票、进站，花了大概三四分钟的时间跑到了站台。还好火车站人不多，要不然妥妥的赶不上了。<br>顺利坐&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144126.html\" target=\"_blank\">上高</a>&nbsp;铁，三个小时到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10440.html\" target=\"_blank\">黄山</a>&nbsp;高铁北站。提前在网上包好三天的用车，出火车站包车的师傅已到达，将我们送往&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;。<br>约一个小时的车程，到达了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;西入口处。</p><p>在网上订好门票，至景区入口处取票后进入&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;，等待客栈的人来接我们去客栈。<br>注：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;景区门票现场购买104，网上94，需要用身份证购买，三天内可以随意出入景区，但一定要和身份证同步使用。<br>这次选择了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;漆零漆陆精品客栈作为&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;的落脚点，从西门进去，沿着南湖往里走，大概十分钟左右就到了，位置比较方便。<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823481\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823481.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/3B/wKgEaVy_3XeALdzWAAGCzcIQbvw73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823494\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823494.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/40/wKgEaVy_3XmANR_XAAHg0JAgAeY12.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823505\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823505.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/44/wKgEaVy_3XuACMShAAMvwuNGBQg98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>放下行李，稍作作息，出去觅食。因为门票三天内可以随意进出，所以选择了景区外的1983餐馆就餐。味道还不错，价格也算可以。四个人点了一个臭鳜鱼、一份土鸡汤、两个蔬菜，美团上的团购价198元。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823519\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823519.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/4B/wKgEaVy_3X6AeGtiAAL9YyEEHwI29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>吃好午饭，从南湖开始，一路南湖书院—敬德堂—月沼—承志堂—……村口&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145805.html\" target=\"_blank\">大树</a>&nbsp;，将&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;大概逛了一圈。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823539\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823539.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/53/wKgEaVy_3YKAWXEUAAPUl7NQsI478.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823549\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823549.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/57/wKgEaVy_3YOAcrYSAAJgfTTbRcw15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>途中经过&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;邮局，习惯性的进去写上一张寄给自己的明信片，并再买一张带回来，算是给大笨猪的，当然由我自己保存。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823562\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823562.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/5F/wKgEaVy_3YeART-3AALCSD8pQRg18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>写好明信片，想起网上看到的屌丝奶茶，于是一路寻寻觅觅，往往返返，终于找到了“&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>&nbsp;奶茶”，尝一尝传说中的屌丝奶茶和牛B奶茶，两者唯一的区别是屌丝奶茶有一点点淡淡的酒味，两款奶茶都比较淡，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66290.html\" target=\"_blank\">和平</a>&nbsp;时喝的略有不同，而且有点咸咸的，和曾经在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13061.html\" target=\"_blank\">新疆</a>&nbsp;喝到的奶茶有几分相似。<br></p><p>再次回到南湖，太阳渐渐落山了，游客也渐渐稀少了，夕阳的余晖也不再如下午的阳光一般刺眼了，此时的古村相对下午而言，多了几分安静。<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823710\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823710.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/8D/wKgEaVy_3aSAeIFIAAEmgXwJKng23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823715\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823715.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/8F/wKgEaVy_3aWASFzfAAFWnFsriSQ76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823720\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823720.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/92/wKgEaVy_3aiADGWEAAJTKZANDW053.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823723\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823723.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/94/wKgEaVy_3amALENNAAFK59M_uo841.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455823728\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823728.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/97/wKgEaVy_3auADWSIAAEUwT_qCPo07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>晚餐选择了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;老街饭店，其实和&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14293.html\" target=\"_blank\">蒙古</a>&nbsp;奶茶是一家。吃饭途中上演了一出小插曲，因为菜单的误导，原本只有腊肉的腊肉煲，我们误以为有腊肉和香肠，于是找老板理论，结果老板解释完之后爽快的答应给我们加了香肠。<br><br>吃饱喝足，看一眼&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10825.html\" target=\"_blank\">宏村</a>&nbsp;的夜。这里没有&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10434.html\" target=\"_blank\">乌镇</a>&nbsp;、凤凰古城一样的灿烂灯光，这里只有星星点灯和串串灯笼。<br>回到客栈，在小院里的秋千椅上坐一会儿，聊聊天、晃晃悠悠甚至悠闲。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823770\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12719/scenery_12470662/455823770.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/9D/wKgEaVy_3a-APsa_AACpRpvwWmI22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>一到这类古镇或古村，就会不由自主的想起大笨猪，想起曾经的那个&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10010.html\" target=\"_blank\">西塘</a>&nbsp;之约。而在小院里还偏偏听到了《可不可以》这首歌，瞬间心里觉得堵得慌。尤其是歌词开头几句：说好带你流浪，而我却半路返航……每次听到这首歌，心里总会特别特别的乱，心情也会瞬间跌入谷底。而在这里听到，更是思绪万千。<br>从&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10010.html\" target=\"_blank\">西塘</a>&nbsp;之约开始，一次次的旅行都不了了之，到最后不再期待与大笨猪的旅行。但只要一提到古镇，还是会不由自主的想起大笨猪，想起约好一起去&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10010.html\" target=\"_blank\">西塘</a>&nbsp;，想起大笨猪曾经说过的那个美好的“假设”。</p>', '2019年04月13日，我向自己预约了这篇游记，当时我说：心心念念已久的 ;黄山 ;、 ;宏村 ;之行终于成行了！春节前就想着去一次 ;黄山 ;和 ;宏村 ;，后来因为时间问题，迟迟未能成行。2月底因一次工作的调整变动，心情低落到了谷底，再加上因为大笨猪的...', '2019-04-13 00:00:00', 5, 1500, 1, '潘大美女', '2019-04-29 10:35:48', '2019-05-06 19:34:03', '宏村-黄山', '宏村', 2, 43, 1);
INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (4, '坐上飞毯到摩洛哥去完成一个“一千零一夜”的神话', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/moluoge1.jpeg', '<p>趁着还有休闲时间，不想停下脚下的步伐，一定要出去走走看看。</p><p>在纠结与&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10053.html\" target=\"_blank\">土耳其</a>&nbsp;的不稳定，只想去一个远点的地方，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a></p><p>这个六月开始对&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;免签的国家定格在我的脑海中：那个阿拉伯神话</p><p>故事里的阿拉丁神灯，一千零一夜的小镇、可以坐在飞毯上穿梭的色彩缤纷</p><p>街道，都可以在这个&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10686.html\" target=\"_blank\">北非</a>&nbsp;国家体验,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;它是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14517.html\" target=\"_blank\">非洲</a>&nbsp;却不似&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14517.html\" target=\"_blank\">非洲</a>&nbsp;，据说它是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14383.html\" target=\"_blank\">欧洲</a>&nbsp;的后花园。</p><p>真的是临时决定的，以前</p><p>做梦都不会想到要去的地方，如今就要去了。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;这个曾经被&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10171.html\" target=\"_blank\">法国</a>&nbsp;殖民过的阿拉伯国家，具有&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14383.html\" target=\"_blank\">欧洲</a>&nbsp;风格的建筑深深吸引着外国游客，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a></p><p>游客很少。因此对于探寻三毛曾经呆过的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16068.html\" target=\"_blank\">撒哈拉沙漠</a>&nbsp;以及她和荷西在那发生的浪漫爱情故事，还有那</p><p>美丽的花儿、围着神秘面纱的女子，都是我要去的理由。</p><p>每个女人都是爱美的，要到那么一个充满神迷、古老的异域国家，衣服肯定是要精雕细选的，</p><p>因为跟团是十天，衣服也要多多的好哦！而且要选色彩亮丽的。</p><p>由于是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14517.html\" target=\"_blank\">非洲</a>&nbsp;，气候炎热，防嗮霜必备。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;信伊斯兰教，很多清真寺，长袖长衣必备，还有墨镜、帽子，伞</p><p>都要带。对了那里的酒店没有拖鞋，没有牙刷牙膏，自己在走之前都要准备好。</p><p>没去之前看了那么多自由行，都说&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;是以阿拉伯语和法语为主，可我们跟团都是用英语交流，看来</p><p>语言不是问题。</p><p>关于行程：</p><p>DAY1&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a>&nbsp;机场集合凌晨起飞</p><p>DAY2&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a></p><p>DAY3&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16077.html\" target=\"_blank\">马拉喀什</a></p><p>DAY4&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113643.html\" target=\"_blank\">瓦尔扎扎特</a></p><p>DAY5托德拉峡谷</p><p>DAY6&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16068.html\" target=\"_blank\">撒哈拉沙漠</a>&nbsp;大门—梅祖卡</p><p>DAY7&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16078.html\" target=\"_blank\">非斯</a></p><p>DAY8&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113733.html\" target=\"_blank\">舍夫沙万</a></p><p>DAY9&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113625.html\" target=\"_blank\">拉巴特</a></p><p>DAY10&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a></p><div id=\"_j_photo_457681885\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681885.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/60/B8/wKgBs1fYA82AGpIeAAddpdNtNL086.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681856\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681856.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/71/EE/wKgBZ1kk21uAdvNRABiKtaBDZh477.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681823\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681823.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/E4/DE/wKgBs1fvuGGAGNsMAAKuEsMIFcU47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681794\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681794.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/DE/97/wKgBs1fZSAWADEb5AAawStU0bPY22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681772\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681772.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/64/A8/wKgBs1fYCXmAQiWTAAS8znJZPCc58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681744\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681744.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/DE/EC/wKgBs1fZSL2ASlFRAAx8gmr6leY22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681714\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681714.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/10/68/wKgBs1f7j0GAM1qUAAkcC6xoduY74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681681\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681681.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/69/4D/wKgBs1fYEDSAPhXFAA0o3PkS3KA44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681607\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681607.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/6A/1C/wKgBs1fYEUqAbOEFAAwhu-bAngk14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681496\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681496.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/C0/wKgBZ1kw1tGAI0ecAAGYR3uXY_870.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681470\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681470.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/6A/E7/wKgBs1fYEkeASWHjAAocOHy9RRQ03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>自己做的视屏，耽误大家几分钟时间，谢谢捧场！</p><p>凌晨1:50分我们在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10208.html\" target=\"_blank\">重庆</a>&nbsp;江北机场坐上&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12035.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡塔尔</a>&nbsp;航空飞往&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;，中间在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;转机的飞机，导游帮我们办好两程登机牌，行李可以直接到目的地，还好方便。经过5个小时的飞行，到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;已经是早晨7:00了，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;是个国际机场，很大很现代，初生的太阳很美。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_457681376\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681376.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/E9/7C/wKgBs1fZW1-AHUZPAAPD17Dqltc65.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>这是在飞机上遇见的空姐，她可&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143425.html\" target=\"_blank\">大方</a>&nbsp;了，我本来是偷拍她，结果她还要求合影！她漂亮吧。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_457681113\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681113.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/E9/BD/wKgBs1fvwNOAc871AAr0qqN1A0E22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681087\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681087.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/3F/9F/wKgBs1fwwcuAZDUBAAJvLs-SOiI63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681066\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681066.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EA/60/wKgBs1fvweCAEFyhAAle77b7P9s60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681042\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681042.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EA/8E/wKgBs1fvwhuAVQ40AAfwKWN2VNo29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457681013\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457681013.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EA/DD/wKgBs1fvwq6AeSVzAAxcKGRWY2Y63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>这个小男孩太萌萌哒了吧，据说在阿拉伯国家不能随意拍小孩，可我还是在经过他母亲的同意下拍了。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_457680972\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680972.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EB/33/wKgBs1fvwyWAOQceAAoWTEkhxSw92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680951\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680951.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/B5/79/wKgBs1fqK6SAWdsSAAmzeMMMRFk79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16137.html\" target=\"_blank\">多哈</a>&nbsp;转机3.5小时。又经过7个小时的飞行，从来没坐过这么长的飞机，可想当我们安全抵达&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;时有多激动！这里的机场不大，需要填写入境卡，过关的速度有点慢，取完行李可以在机场换&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;币。</p><p>1美元=9.25元【每天汇率不一样】，还可以领一张当地的电话卡，凭护照免费领取30分钟的通话、30分钟流量，一般买2个G,20迪拉姆，一个星期够了。如需更多流量，可到市区买。一出机场就有一排排白色的棚子搭起的过道，都是接机的，举着“UNIWAY-皇家旅游”牌子的是一个微胖的女导游，还是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>人也。</p><p>马上就开始&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;的行程了是比较紧也。我们这个团只有17人，车子有宽松，可以一人占两位!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/113734.html\" target=\"_blank\">卡萨布兰卡</a>&nbsp;是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12033.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩洛哥</a>&nbsp;一座以海而建、最大的白色城市，比较现代。即是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10686.html\" target=\"_blank\">北非</a>&nbsp;最大最重要的港口，它也是由一部电影“&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10686.html\" target=\"_blank\">北非</a>&nbsp;谍影”而出名。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_457680853\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680853.html\"><img src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/E9/8E/wKgBs1fZW5CAUtLKAAlzYxaUtpY63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680824\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680824.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/E9/DC/wKgBs1fZXDKAKd_NAAF8UX1y53k24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680796\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680796.html\"><img src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/EA/19/wKgBs1fZXHWAZgpyAAHKlWUADFE02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680768\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680768.html\"><img src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/38/B9/wKgBs1fwtSyAMW24AAoDSAmJlok71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>我们到旅店换好衣服，大约5:30分，就去参观市区的【鸽子广场】广场不是很大，鸽子多，很多大人带着小孩来玩。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_457680636\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680636.html\"><img src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/39/0A/wKgBs1fwtbaALRV2AAz74ZkGEcs38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680607\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680607.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/A6/39/wKgBs1hk2nKAA8YEAAxAip6loRs15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680583\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680583.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/A6/2D/wKgBs1hk2liAREcvAAi3BICTlXo89.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680499\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680499.html\"><img src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/39/4C/wKgBs1fwtkyARy0JAAjm_NjSqrM27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680465\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680465.html\"><img src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/39/5C/wKgBs1fwtnSAYVfQAAj8ZgF4rYk48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680437\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680437.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/FC/6A/wKgBs1f7dt-AJiH4AAvl6gpAUBw35.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_457680415\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/12033/scenery_12495306/457680415.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/FC/A2/wKgBs1f7dyGAC3G3AAqTn7WzFic28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>这是根据，电影《&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10686.html\" target=\"_blank\">北非</a>&nbsp;谍影》还原的餐馆---Rick\'sCafe.门卫很帅吧，我们在这间豪华的餐厅享受了贵族</p>', '趁着还有休闲时间，不想停下脚下的步伐，一定要出去走走看看。在纠结与 ;土耳其 ;的不稳定，只想去一个远点的地方， ;摩洛哥这个六月开始对 ;中国 ;免签的国家定格在我的脑海中：那个阿拉伯神话故事里的阿拉丁神灯，一千零一夜的小镇、可以坐在飞毯上穿梭的色彩缤纷...', '2017-08-04 00:00:00', 7, 3600, 1, '潘大美女', '2019-04-29 10:43:02', '2019-05-06 19:30:31', '摩洛哥', '摩洛哥', 2, 22, 1);
INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (5, '一座远远超乎你想像的城市～江城武汉', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/wuhan.jpeg', '<div><h2>鉴证网络传说~</h2></div><p>一直听说（姐之前一直是单身狗&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/79.png\">&nbsp;）旅行可以看出一个男人的真正内在，情侣旅行之后面临的就是分手，于是决定（已是恋爱中的小姐姐）两个人适不适合在一起来一次旅行就知道啦。。。。。。<br><br>都不是绝对的啦，两个人正处在热恋期就因为一次旅行就分手了？傻不傻！傻！<br><br>不过为了旅行顺便考验一下还是可以的，Tina小姐姐就是这样的，最后亲身经验告诉大家增进感情这个是真的&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/20.png\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/20.png\">&nbsp;<br>我们来了~江城~&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455823904\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455823904.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/2E/EE/wKgEaVy_3c2AYwP2AAm2UclDZAI93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5426285.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>黄鹤楼</a></div><p><br></p><div><h2>没有期待便是惊喜~</h2></div><p>起初对&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;的印象&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/93.png\">&nbsp;火炉 火炉 火炉 热干面 完liao。。。。。。<br>给我印象最深的是出租司机不绕远，人热情得很，附带导游讲解还推荐给我们一条美食街（相比之下<br>户部巷弱爆了。。。）~<br><br>交通:<br>乘坐G403&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;西到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;，历时四个小时左右到达&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;站~<br>出站第一感觉，我kao真的比&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;热很多。。。还等什么呢。。脱吧~<br><br>酒店：<br>酒店选在武昌区户部巷附近一家叫纽宾凯君缘酒店（某点评上评价很高），4号换乘2号线抵达，半小时抵达，距离还好，酒店门前就是公交车站（一次没坐过）~<br>房间偏小，卫生有一点点小瑕疵，不过晚上很安静，无早（可能&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;的过早太丰富啦）~<br><br>接下来让我赞美一下这座江城～<br><br>城市很干净~绿植做得好~超级喜欢&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;的绿~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455444345\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455444345.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DD/B3/wKgEaVy-sJiAOYPmABBYks8tZfE76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455444346\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455444346.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DD/BF/wKgEaVy-sJ2AGHHFAA1Ys_G45b846.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉</a></div><p>景点分布近~<br>这是曹先生做的行程，惊喜也有点小感动&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/39.png\">&nbsp;，偷偷做的哦~<br>红色框框是第一天行程，基本完成；蓝色框框是第二天行程，古德寺换成了归元禅寺；黑色框框就是个摆设，因为第二天晚上就开始下雨。。。<br>虽然这次没有去成光谷步行街（没有跟街舞亮亮偶遇），不过有遗憾才会有下次的相聚嘛~<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455445177\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455445177.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DE/6B/wKgEaVy-sOeAGkcsAANJpn3Ulzc937.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>北京</a></div><p><br>这张是曹先生的作品之地铁半偷拍（虽然有点胖，眼神有点奇怪），他很喜欢，我也一样&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/3.png\">&nbsp;~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455415721\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455415721.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/9F/96/wKgEaVy-m8-AAa-qAAWZHsKQMPo79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/73862520.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉地铁</a></div><p>物美价廉~<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;地铁起步价“2元”良心啊！！！<br>没有纸币和硬币的蜂友们不要担心，可以扫码支付哟~<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;地铁比&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;先进的是有电子屏幕报站，很适合外地游客~<br>重点提醒：地铁站内有饮水设备，切勿当洗手盆~<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455965292\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455965292.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/EE/A5/wKgEaVzAKXKAdfQ_AAEvrEohKOY15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6936813.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉站</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455965293\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455965293.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/EE/A6/wKgEaVzAKXKAdGEsAAGevtj2E1o19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6936813.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉站</a></div><p>可以坐轮渡到江滩，也可以做地铁黄浦路地铁站下车步行走到江滩，叫车也很方便（主要起步价10元，再一次良心啊）~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455381810\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455381810.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/63/7B/wKgEaVy-h3mAL1VOAAaosRSE8Ls38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3302431.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武昌江滩</a></div><p>1.5元的轮渡，可以站在甲板上感受长江（风很大，头发吹的那叫个凌乱&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/12.png\">&nbsp;）~<br>一层是电瓶车的底盘，都会上二楼，天气暖一定要去外面，可以站在甲板上观赏&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;江滩的夜景，迎面吹来的江风，还有船尾随风飘扬的五星红旗~</p><div><div></div><div><div><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5803.html\">武汉长江大桥</a></div></div></div><p>坐车偶然看到了计划要去吃的热干面，想不到一早上赵师傅就这么多排队的，还好我们没有去排，具体什么味道不晓得呀，这么多排队的味道应该差不了，下次去尝尝~<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456914487\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/456914487.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/A0/90/wKgEaVy-nA2AMJAfAA4GqTTVess79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455382954\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455382954.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/65/E5/wKgEaVy-iHKAd6_dAAwjQ_liM6k79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6943004.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>赵师傅</a></div><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;的美食会让你上瘾~<br>一大早本来想去品尝赵师傅，结果走到这家小店，迎面扑来的香味让我俩挪不动脚步，立马决定就这家啦&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/7.png\">&nbsp;~<br>一份热干面4元，一根油条1.5元&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36.png\">&nbsp;感动到哭~吃货的我们当然是牛杂热干面啦，哈哈~味道超级棒，蛋酒很香很清淡，早餐吃的很幸福，出发当天曹先生冒着雨去买，小感动哟~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455382513\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455382513.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/64/F2/wKgEaVy-iA2AXIC0AAqAwNb2DeA20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>武汉</a></div><p>在这个位置看到好几对拍婚纱照，沾沾喜气~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455386669\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455386669.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6A/75/wKgEaVy-ineAJELrAAs8ahFHerM86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/35814.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>江汉路步行街</a></div><p>江滩附近看到这个井盖，好看的，可见城市规划，美腻~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455386670\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455386670.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6A/7C/wKgEaVy-inyADcQrAA0yZJCp8cw04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/35814.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>江汉路步行街</a></div><div><h2>人们口中的户部巷~</h2></div><p>每座城市都有一条美食街和 一条步行街，看了好几天马蜂窝，心心念的户部巷&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/91.png\"></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456267782\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/456267782.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DF/9F/wKgEaVzBLyiAJwAmAAcJVwLklWw46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>军运会&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;整体美化，听美食街老板说2天后就封了（心里暗暗自喜，还好赶上了），不过可能这个原因跟我想象中差距很大~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455388878\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455388878.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6D/51/wKgEaVy-i32ADwD8ABAcmrvj9PU84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>米酒味，不过喝起来黏黏糊糊的不喜欢，绿豆汤很畅销没品尝~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455442439\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455442439.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DA/BB/wKgEaVy-r9GAZI9XAAqVZkGVfwI29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>吃过&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16215.html\" target=\"_blank\">东北</a>&nbsp;的、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html\" target=\"_blank\">山东</a>&nbsp;的、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12871.html\" target=\"_blank\">福建</a>&nbsp;的、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html\" target=\"_blank\">上海</a>&nbsp;的。。。我还是好想吃&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10466.html\" target=\"_blank\">长沙</a>&nbsp;臭豆腐&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/7.png\">&nbsp;~<br>这么大个锅炸这么几块，不排队才怪，能不能长点心&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/16.png\">&nbsp;~<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456268107\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/456268107.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/E0/99/wKgEaVzBL4aAH3ktAAaBKR8sEik79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455442440\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455442440.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/DA/CD/wKgEaVy-r9WAKpJTAAsncFo-cCQ20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>走了一圈对户部巷真的没什么特别感觉，可能军运会的缘故？？？被这四位老奶奶逗笑了，这宣传模式。。。所以我消费了，不过樱花饼吃起来跟玫瑰花饼傻傻分不清楚~</p><div><div></div><div><div><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\">户部巷小吃一条街</a></div></div></div><div id=\"_j_photo_455388879\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455388879.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6D/62/wKgEaVy-i4GAMvzzAAp7y6HJgSE76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>排队第一家“一根排骨”，等待时间超级漫长，无意中发现这是商家对策，为了制造排队景象，竟然还有老阿姨组队的吃托&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/16.png\"></p><div id=\"_j_photo_455390324\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455390324.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6E/AC/wKgEaVy-jBWAMJ8NAAo5AkjFtMk54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div><p>三种味道：番茄、经典香辣、黑椒~<br>这一排是放了不少根，架不住他烤的慢啊，那小眼神紧盯着后面队伍的进展~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_455390325\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10133/scenery_12486478/455390325.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/6E/B7/wKgEaVy-jBqATYxiABC6eLZkMW485.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6767.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>户部巷小吃一条街</a></div>', '鉴证网络传说~一直听说（姐之前一直是单身狗 ; ;）旅行可以看出一个男人的真正内在，情侣旅行之后面临的就是分手，于是决定（已是恋爱中的小姐姐）两个人适不适合在一起来一次旅行就知道啦。。。。。。都不是绝对的啦，两个人正处在热恋期就因为一次旅行就分手了？傻不傻...', '2019-04-12 00:00:00', 5, 2000, 1, '潘大美女', '2019-04-29 10:53:12', '2019-05-07 10:08:39', '武汉', '武汉', 2, 10, 1);
INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (7, '诸神的故乡——雅典（2019-03-28）', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/yadain.jpeg', '<div><h2>诸神的故乡——雅典</h2></div><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17211.html\" target=\"_blank\">爱琴海</a>&nbsp;。简简单单的几个字，却足以拨动人的心弦。在这方土地上诸神曾上演过多少爱恨情仇。看金沙似的阳光撒在苏格拉底、柏拉图曾走过的小径上，寻觅一方叫做&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17211.html\" target=\"_blank\">爱琴海</a>&nbsp;的浑然天成的蓝，那是一个根深蒂固的梦。<br><br>到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145202.html\" target=\"_blank\">南欧</a>&nbsp;旅行首先要谒见的自然是诸神的故乡——&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;。&nbsp;<br><br>当&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;娜女神和海神波塞冬为争做&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;保护神而斗智，波塞冬变出战马，而&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;娜奉上橄榄枝。结果众神一致认为橄榄对人类更有用，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;娜因此成为这座城市的保护神，这座城市也因此而得名&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>。<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;，这诸神的故乡，我们处处可以看到神话的留存。<br><br>曾在无数明信片上见到过神庙，但当它真真切切地出现在眼前时，那宏伟的立柱、沧桑的历史、低调却不可侵犯的感觉依然会扑面而来，令人在它面前屏住呼吸。在那古老深邃的文化面前，神庙仿若一座精密的时光机器，可以带我们回到神话时代，与诸神一起直面最深远的智慧。&nbsp;<br><br>六少女立柱虽历经世代却依然美丽，她们长裙束胸，优雅轻盈，虽然作用是为了代替&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/20924.html\" target=\"_blank\">石柱</a>&nbsp;顶起石顶，但亭亭玉立的身姿只会让人觉得她们是美丽的精灵附体而成。建筑师为了体现少女的美感，在少女颈后保留了一缕浓厚的厚发，再在头顶加上花蓝，头顶花蓝颈披秀发的少女在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;成了一个智慧的奇迹。<br><br>奥林匹克剧场天然的舞台，岩石早已风化得斑驳，那是大自然唱的最动听的歌，若是在这里唱歌，大概可以称为天籁之音吧？<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045431\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045431.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/29/wKgEaVzAWZCAKBWDAAsEd6tQfSg03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><p>世界艺术宝库中著名的帕特农神庙矗立在卫城的最高点，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;卫城古城堡的中心， 又名巴特农神庙，是一座巍峨的矩形建筑物。<br><br>神庙历经两千多年的沧桑之变，如今庙顶已坍塌，雕像荡然无存，浮雕剥蚀严重，但从巍然屹立的柱廊中，还可以看出神庙当年的丰姿。</p><div><h2>希腊——欧洲文明的发源地</h2></div><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14383.html\" target=\"_blank\">欧洲</a>&nbsp;最资深的文明古国，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/60296.html\" target=\"_blank\">克里特</a>&nbsp;岛在公元前3000年已出现了米诺斯文化，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/60297.html\" target=\"_blank\">伯罗奔尼撒</a>&nbsp;半岛在公元前1600年已出现了迈锡尼文化。同样，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;也是资深古城，在公元前一千多年，<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;已是古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的核心城市，有文字记载的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;历史为3千多年。<br><br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;不仅是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的首都，也是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;最大的城市。其实&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;并不大，面积仅有412平方公里，人口不足80万。整个&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;也没多大，人口1100万，面积只有13万余平方公里。然而，在古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的辉煌时代，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的国土不仅包括了巴尔干半岛、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17211.html\" target=\"_blank\">爱琴海</a>&nbsp;诸岛，也包括了现在的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10051.html\" target=\"_blank\">意大利</a>&nbsp;半岛及&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10170.html\" target=\"_blank\">西西里</a>&nbsp;岛，还包括了现在的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10686.html\" target=\"_blank\">北非</a>&nbsp;和西亚。<br><br>作为&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14383.html\" target=\"_blank\">欧洲</a>&nbsp;文明的发源地，古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的辉煌成遍及哲学、文学、数学、建筑、绘画、雕刻等等诸多领域。古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的衰落始于公元前546年波斯帝国的兴起，而古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;灭亡的标志是公元前30年被&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10063.html\" target=\"_blank\">罗马</a>&nbsp;帝国吞并。自1460年起，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;又被兴起于&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html\" target=\"_blank\">亚洲</a>&nbsp;西部的伊斯兰教奥斯曼帝国统治，直至&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;独立战争（1821～1829）。<br><br>友情提醒：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;是四大文明古国之一，去之前多做功课，了解一下著名历史古迹的由来、搜集一些经典故事，会令你欣赏古代建筑的过程变得别有趣味！ 推荐阅读老友horus的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;旅游攻略 “&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;-西方文明起源地”，该攻略对古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;文明，特别是古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的建筑艺术进行了较有深度的研究和叙述，一定会对你了解&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;的历史或去&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;旅游大有帮助的，相比我的这篇游记只能算是走马观花、浮光掠影玩玩而已。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456047824\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456047824.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/5A/FE/wKgEaVzAWsSARMMeAAiPoFiFJr843.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><p>议会大厦和宪法广场。议会大厦建于1836年，原来是王宫。前面的宪法广场是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;市中心广场，也是<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;进行各种重大政治和国事活动的场所。广场上无名战士纪念碑前每小时一次的卫兵换岗仪式吸引了大批游客。</p><div><h2>我们在雅典的游览内容</h2></div><p>　　从&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html\" target=\"_blank\">北京</a>&nbsp;到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;，无论从哪个国家中转都需要花费十多个小时甚至更长。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;城区很小，但古迹较多。我个人认为应该花一整天的时间细细观赏。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63538.html\" target=\"_blank\">比如</a>&nbsp;帕特农神庙，供奉&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;的保护神&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;娜的地方。上千年历史，恢宏壮观。1687年&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11083.html\" target=\"_blank\">威尼斯</a>&nbsp;人与&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10053.html\" target=\"_blank\">土耳其</a>&nbsp;人作战时，神庙遭到破坏。19世纪下半叶，曾对神庙进行过部分修复，已无法恢复原貌，现仅留有一座&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/20924.html\" target=\"_blank\">石柱</a>&nbsp;林立的外壳，就变成今天这个样子 —— 不过依然是气势雄伟，令观者无论在身体上还是心理上都需要仰望。卫城的夜景据说非常美，小山顶上明亮灯光映射出黄灿灿的城池（有明信片为证）……。可惜我们是参团旅游， 这样的美景都被错过！还有个人计划参观考古博物馆 ，14点半结束团队游，应该有时间去，但团队不少游客吵吵早点回去，结果下午4点半就集体回酒店了，集合时间如能放在18时，或是住的酒店离的近些，我就自行前往了，打轰轰的团队，个人想深度游览是有一定难度的。<br><br>我们在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;的游览内容包括：卫城、宪法广场、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/135194.html\" target=\"_blank\">普拉</a>&nbsp;卡历史街区、新古典主义三大建筑&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;大学、国家图书馆等。毫无疑问，这些游览内容中，重头戏当然是卫城，因为&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;的卫城是<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;最杰出的古建筑群。<br><br>卫城是一组壮观的建筑群，主要包括山门、露天剧场、帕特农神庙、埃雷赫修神庙（又译伊瑞克提翁神庙）。<br><br>卫城的山门相&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145300.html\" target=\"_blank\">当雄</a>&nbsp;伟，就坡而建，呈不对称排列，屋顶亦断开。山门虽然已经破旧不堪，但我们仍能看出它精美的设计，山门正面有6根多立克式的高大的柱子（又称男性柱）。在经过这些柱子时，还能看见一些残缺的石质屋顶，以前的屋顶曾镀过金，并且有彩绘。<br><br>露天剧场十分气派。露天剧场的学名是阿迪库斯音乐厅，位于卫城入口南侧，建于&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10063.html\" target=\"_blank\">罗马</a>&nbsp;时代。这座可容纳6000多人的户外剧场，在任何一个座位都能听清舞台上演员的台词。 剧场现在仍然作为夏季露天音乐会和戏剧表演的场所。<br><br>帕特农神庙是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;卫城主体建筑，为歌颂&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;战胜波斯侵略者的胜利而建。神庙始建于公元前447年，正式启用是在公元前438年，借着盛大的帕那太耐节奉献给&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;娜。帕特农神庙曾经被用作金库，天主教堂，清真寺。1687年9月28日神庙被&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10053.html\" target=\"_blank\">土耳其</a>&nbsp;军当火药库，堆积的火药不幸被&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11083.html\" target=\"_blank\">威尼斯</a>&nbsp;军队炮击中，引发的爆炸严重损毁了庙体还有雕刻。<br><br>埃雷赫修神庙 ，位于帕特农神庙北面，建于公元前421年至405年。该庙内有三个神殿，分别供奉&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>的主神宙斯、海神波塞冬、铁匠之神赫菲斯托斯。比较独特的是，埃雷赫修神庙是用美女雕像作为立柱，既富有创意又富有美感。<br><br>当我们在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;卫城游览的时候，天阴，狂风大作。拍的照片灰蒙蒙的，如有蓝天白云做背景，才能更好地衬托出卫城的恢弘气势。<br><br>我们自己去了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/135194.html\" target=\"_blank\">普拉</a>&nbsp;卡历史街区和新古典主义三大建筑参观。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;著名的三大建筑：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院、&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;大学、国家图书馆。这三座出自同一个设计师之手的建筑并排连在一起，显得有点拥挤。从建筑外形来看，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;大学和国家图书馆比较一般，最出彩的是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院，该建筑于1859年8月2日奠基，中间因战乱停止了数年，直到1885年建设完成。其实，这座建筑刚建成的时候是作为国家博物馆，直到1926年&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院成立才被归于科学院。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院被称作是一座新古典主义建筑，所谓新古典主义，是一种多元化的建筑风格。这种建筑风格的特点是，借鉴古典的华贵造型，但简化繁杂的雕饰，同时选择现代的材质，最终呈现出古典与简约相融合的新时尚。<br><br>这天比较感兴趣的还有无名战士纪念碑和守护士兵的换岗仪式。纪念碑是为1823年独立战争以及此后历次战争中牺牲的战士而建，碑体刻有躺在灵柩上的士兵浮雕，两侧用&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;文分别刻着古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;历史学家修昔底德的两句著名格言：青山处处埋忠骨，白云无名做灵床。卫兵持枪昂首挺胸于碑的两侧，每整点时分进行换岗仪式表演，给人一种亦庄亦谐的好感，换岗仪式总能吸引大批的观众。站岗只有两个卫兵，别看人少，换岗仪式的花样可并不少，挺有看头的，也很有趣。卫兵的服装有点滑稽，尤其是鞋子和帽子都比较怪，而卫兵的动作更怪，整个换岗过程大概持续十几分钟。<br><br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;卫城的山门<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045426\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045426.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/21/wKgEaVzAWYyAQh5tAAkB4waPjrQ50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><p></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045427\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045427.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/22/wKgEaVzAWY2ALksHAAc2XkNa4-473.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045432\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045432.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/2B/wKgEaVzAWZCAaA0VAAfz_M8mUtA19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045440\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045440.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/3C/wKgEaVzAWZeAC-drAApjkEpgAkY91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045436\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045436.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/33/wKgEaVzAWZOANe8hAAhy-PDn-ZA52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456044840\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456044840.html\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/57/49/wKgEaVzAWTSAew8eAAmGoMqeEtY30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045437\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045437.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/33/wKgEaVzAWZSAeczrAAvDw_1s5zs19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045430\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045430.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/26/wKgEaVzAWY-AZHM2AAXxrzhxepY08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/19023.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>卫城山门</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045441\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045441.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/3D/wKgEaVzAWZiADIPmAAkc-OoAWgg11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><p>帕特农神庙<br><br>曾在无数明信片上见到过神庙，但当它真真切切地出现在眼前时，那宏伟的立柱、沧桑的历史、低调却不可侵犯的感觉依然会扑面而来，令人在它面前屏住呼吸，把我们带回到神话时代，与诸神一起直面最深远的智慧。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045431\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045431.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/29/wKgEaVzAWZCAKBWDAAsEd6tQfSg03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045439\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045439.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/3A/wKgEaVzAWZeAZfzdAAllQiyB7FY56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045435\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045435.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/30/wKgEaVzAWZKARYAAAAiOwzktuM067.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>帕特农神庙</a></div><p>远处在汽车上拍摄的卫城。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456047312\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456047312.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/5A/01/wKgEaVzAWmWAS9tjAAa8vW7rbmI95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>雅典卫城</a></div><p>埃雷赫修神庙<br><br>六少女立柱虽历经世代却依然美丽，她们长裙束胸，优雅轻盈，虽然作用是为了代替&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/20924.html\" target=\"_blank\">石柱</a>&nbsp;顶起石顶，但亭亭玉立的身姿只会让人觉得她们是美丽的精灵附体而成，头顶花蓝颈披秀发的少女在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;成了一个智慧的奇迹。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045433\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045433.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/2C/wKgEaVzAWZGAR0fiAAeZORNqsUY87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/77994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>伊瑞克提翁神庙</a></div><p></p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045434\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045434.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/2F/wKgEaVzAWZKAEpQkAAlzj7pi3lw22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/77994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>伊瑞克提翁神庙</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045428\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045428.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/24/wKgEaVzAWY6AJxXOAAdd0szCADQ24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/77994.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>伊瑞克提翁神庙</a></div><p>露天剧场<br><br>（此段文字引自百度）&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;的狄奥尼索斯剧场建于公元前6世纪，是最古老的露天剧场。剧场位于&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;卫城南侧，是有两个半圆形的剧场，由门廊相连，充分体现了古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;人对艺术的热爱。在这足以容纳17000人的剧场里曾经上演的Odium of Herodes Attius剧场现在仍然作为夏季露天音乐会和戏剧表演的场所，东侧的酒神剧场作为景点向游客开放，该剧场建于公元前5世纪，最早是向酒神祈祷的地方。<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64188.html\" target=\"_blank\">大名</a>&nbsp;鼎鼎的酒神剧场上演了无数的戏剧，最出名的是四大悲剧。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456262282\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456262282.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/D0/E4/wKgEaVzBK3aAKpDyAAMIIQFea6w68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><p>露天剧场全景图（引自网络）</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456045420\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045420.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/11/wKgEaVzAWYiAdciKAAw5u_u87rA32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045418\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045418.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/0B/wKgEaVzAWYaAYHp6ABHiqyx8_zA00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045417\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045417.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/09/wKgEaVzAWYWAYQ6CABCjVbfB37M86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>雅典卫城</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045423\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045423.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/19/wKgEaVzAWYqARk9nAAv_iDoZzbU17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045416\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045416.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/07/wKgEaVzAWYSAHqO9AAsfQuqUoOY23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>雅典卫城</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045421\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045421.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/13/wKgEaVzAWYiAXtK6AAvy6zyiGYE93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045422\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045422.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/16/wKgEaVzAWYmAY2aFAAnBYdTNm4446.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456045419\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456045419.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/0E/wKgEaVzAWYeAbe_NAA7F2RuRd9c83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a target=\"_blank\"><i></i>园形剧场</a></div><p>宪法广场、议会大厦和无名战士纪念碑同在一地。原是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;第一代国王奥托王宫的议会大厦，自1931年改造后至今仍在使用；大厦前的宪法广场因“&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;宪法”而得名；正对大厦有一块大石碑，为著名的无名战士纪念碑。东向不远处，便是1897年建造的弥散着新古典式建筑风格的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;总统府。宪法广场向西，沿路就能看到三&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63611.html\" target=\"_blank\">大新</a>&nbsp;古典主义建筑，即&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;科学院、国家图书馆和&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11143.html\" target=\"_blank\">雅典</a>&nbsp;大学。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456046506\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046506.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/F7/wKgEaVzAWf6AFe89AAc0pz3tPmM54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456046516\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046516.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/59/04/wKgEaVzAWgeAPVShAAy6vvr9Tr853.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456047293\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456047293.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/59/D6/wKgEaVzAWlaAWf8KAAT5bntnp3c86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456047292\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456047292.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/59/D4/wKgEaVzAWlaAGAeFAApL-2S71uw53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18812.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>雅典卫城</a></div><p>无名战士纪念碑和守护士兵的换岗仪式。纪念碑是为1823年独立战争以及此后历次战争中牺牲的战士而建，碑体刻有躺在灵柩上的士兵浮雕，两侧用&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;文分别刻着古&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10168.html\" target=\"_blank\">希腊</a>&nbsp;历史学家修昔底德的两句著名格言：青山处处埋忠骨，白云无名做灵床。卫兵持枪昂首挺胸于碑的两侧，每整点时分进行换岗仪式表演，给人一种亦庄亦谐的好感，换岗仪式总能吸引大批的观众。站岗只有两个卫兵，别看人少，换岗仪式的花样可并不少，挺有看头的，也很有趣。卫兵的服装有点滑稽，尤其是鞋子和帽子都比较怪，而卫兵的动作更怪，整个换岗过程大概持续十几分钟。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_456046508\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046508.html\"><img src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/FA/wKgEaVzAWgCAOIONAAwBk54858U69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456046509\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046509.html\"><img src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/FB/wKgEaVzAWgGAC89tAAmM7ypb4hQ88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456046515\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046515.html\"><img src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/59/03/wKgEaVzAWgaABxcyAAuvZcRP7mg82.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_456046512\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10168/scenery_12481558/456046512.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/58/FF/wKgEaVzAWgOAb6M9AAndLh12pqg72.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/18810.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>宪法广场</a></div>', '诸神的故乡——雅典希腊 ;， ;雅典 ;， ;爱琴海 ;。简简单单的几个字，却足以拨动人的心弦。在这方土地上诸神曾上演过多少爱恨情仇。看金沙似的阳光撒在苏格拉底、柏拉图曾走过的小径上，寻觅一方叫做 ;爱琴海 ;的浑然天成的蓝，那是一个根深蒂固的梦。到 ;南...', '2019-03-27 00:00:00', 14, 10000, 1, '潘大美女', '2019-04-29 10:59:59', '2019-05-07 20:49:37', '希腊-雅典', '希腊', 2, 16, 2);
INSERT INTO `strategy` VALUES (8, '在世界最北之北追寻极光之旅——俄罗斯', 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/eluosi1.jpeg', '<p>印象中的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;，世界上面积最大的国家，普金好帅，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;人好美，就是这么肤浅的印象，哈哈哈<br>en~~~其实并没有想法去踏足这个国家<br><br>偶然间看到一篇旅行游记写&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;看极光，被深深地吸引住了<br>刚好&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a>&nbsp;往返&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;机票价格很美丽<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;之行就是在这样的契机下被勾勒了出来<br>然后成为了我迄今为止最难忘，最棒的一次旅行。<br><br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;的12天，我在<br>北冰洋边邂逅了一场叹为观止的绚烂极光<br>世界的尽头与雪山，海，厚雪铺满的沙滩融为一体<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/139973.html\" target=\"_blank\">马林</a>&nbsp;斯基剧院里欣赏古典芭蕾的高雅艺术<br>地下艺术宫殿感受曾经强大辉煌的红色帝国<br><br><br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_426929117\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426929117.html\"><img src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/AC/wKgBEFxezm2AdPTqABDwcbS4uxs96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426929125\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426929125.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/AF/wKgBEFxezm-AeAkYABJmbXH5T8441.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934022\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934022.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D1/A9/wKgBZ1xe0LOAL2lzAAcdMMuyapo39.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/34194748.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>蒂瑞贝尔斯基海滩露营地餐厅</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934032\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934032.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D1/AA/wKgBZ1xe0LSACSlQAAdNDROvDns29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/34194748.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>蒂瑞贝尔斯基海滩露营地餐厅</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426929112\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426929112.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/AB/wKgBEFxezmyAWYWYAA5ct-jyTMw76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div><h2>行程安排</h2></div><p>1月22日—2月1日&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;往返 2934元<br>1月22日 19：50 —22：00&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html\" target=\"_blank\">广州</a>&nbsp;（宿&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html\" target=\"_blank\">广州</a>&nbsp;）<br>1月23日 10：25—19：25&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html\" target=\"_blank\">广州</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;<br>1月23日 22：25—01：05&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;580元<br>1月24日 13：00&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;—捷里别尔卡 （Y.Taxi 打车 2500rub）<br>1月26日 20：25—22：25&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;573元<br>1月29日 21：36—07：19&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;（软卧火车200元）<br>2月1日 21：40—10：50&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;<br>2月2日 19：00— 21：05&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10133.html\" target=\"_blank\">武汉</a>&nbsp;—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a>&nbsp;<br><br>上面写的都是当地时间，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;比&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;慢5个小时。</p><div><h2>前期准备</h2></div><p>1. 签证<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;跟团不需要签证，自由行需要签证，在淘宝订的（600多元），&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;签证很容易的。<br>准备好护照，两张2寸白底近半年照，填写申请书一起邮寄给淘宝商家。记得要选择有邀请函的，因为去&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;自由行都需要邀请函，有可能入境会查。<br>但是入境只给护照和签证就行，签证上就可以看出是哪里出具的邀请函，其他的要什么给什么，把已经订好的酒店预订单打印出来备用。<br>2. 订酒店<br>（特别推荐&nbsp;<img src=\"http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/97.png\">&nbsp;）捷里别尔卡：蒂瑞贝尔斯基海滩露营地（就是首图的红房子，一共只有八间房，一间房里有两个上下铺共四个床位，一晚上700多元，要提前几个月预定，是当地最火的房子，从房间的窗户就可以看见外面的湖，我就是在房间里看到的极光，小镇上只有它一家餐馆，基本要吃饭都会到这里来）<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;：选择涅瓦大街附近<br><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;： 选择红场附近<br>3.货币<br>提前几天在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;银行预约10000卢布的现金，相当于1066元人民币。<br>其实在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;都是可以刷卡的，而且刷卡的汇率比现金划算很多，不过大部分只能刷VISA\\MASTER卡，银联能刷的地方没有那么多。所以最好准备一张VISA\\MASTER卡。现金用作打车、乘坐雪地摩托车等。我还准备了一张&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10035.html\" target=\"_blank\">成都</a>&nbsp;银行金卡备用，以防现金不够（在外取现每月前三次不收手续费）<br>4.通讯<br>飞猪上买的MTC的卡，11天无限流量含通话，信号非常好，直接插卡就能用。<br>5.天气;衣着;物品<br>一月，是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;全年最冷的月份，我只能说是真的冷。捷里是最冷的，早上10点天才刚刚亮，下午4点天已经开始黑了，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;要稍微没有那么冷。<br>帽子，围巾，口罩，手套都是必备的。手套一定要买可以玩手机的手套，裸手几秒钟就会冻僵。<br>雪地靴必须是防水防滑，最好买大一到两个尺码的，基本是穿两双羊毛袜，一双羊毛垫再加上暖宝宝&nbsp;<br>外套是必须是羽绒服，内搭保暖内衣，羽绒内衣，毛衣。裤子穿的秋裤，羊绒打底裤，长毛线裙。<br>暖宝宝必备（脚底专用暖宝宝，一般暖宝宝）买了超多，没有用完，每天基本只贴一次（脚底，肚子，后背，膝盖都贴）。<br>6.APP<br>Google Maps：必备！不管是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;盘综复杂的地铁还是世界尽头的区域定位，都离不开它。<br>TripAdvisor猫途鹰：我们在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;吃的餐厅都是在国内提前用这个APP搜索好。<br>Aurora\\Aurora fcst： 检测极光的必备软件。三天内的检测都是很准的。<br>Yandex.taxi：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;的滴滴，非常好用，价格比出租车便宜。<br><br><br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_428408038\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/428408038.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/0B/D7/wKgBEFxi1HyANEtsAANurDzJ-ww95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>这是我这次去用的所有APP。<br>所带物品：护照+签证+邀请函、身份证、货币（人民币+卢布）、信用卡/银行卡<br>充电宝2个，保温杯，转换头（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;为两孔圆形），旅行烧水壶，插线板</p><div><h2>需要提前买好的票</h2></div><p>1.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;的夜火车票<br>首先登录&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html\" target=\"_blank\">俄罗斯</a>&nbsp;铁路官网：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://eng.rzd.ru/\" target=\"_blank\">http://eng.rzd.ru/</a>&nbsp;<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444906451\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444906451.html\"><img src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/9B/C8/wKgEaVygw5WAELyTAAEofVVztpA04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>登录后可以选择起点站和终点站，以及日期和时间范围。<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444907308\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444907308.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/9C/5D/wKgEaVygw9mABL5fAAK1MxF_52885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>常用的旅游目的地像&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11155.html\" target=\"_blank\">莫斯科</a>&nbsp;Moscow，&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15338.html\" target=\"_blank\">圣彼得堡</a>&nbsp;St. Petersburg，它在下面有，点击就行。<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444907898\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444907898.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/9D/01/wKgEaVygxB-ALhPBAAMzdJ702Jo56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>最好是选择晚上出发，早上到的，在火车上睡一觉就到达了。后面的1299就是费用，选2-cl就可以，3-cl是开放的没有房间门的。<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444910721\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444910721.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/9F/59/wKgEaVygxS6AN_TsAAJl2LEmHQM57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>蓝色的表示可以选的，灰色是已经卖完的。<br>接下来需要填旅客信息。第一行 第一项 “Last Name” 是姓，第二项 “First Name”是名，懂英文的驴友这问题不大。第三项里填中间名，像我们&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;人没有，填“-”。你点在框里它也同样会提示你。第二行依次是性别，男的选“Male”，女的选“Female”，生日用下拉菜单选，格式是“日 . 月 . 年”。最关键的是第三个框“The State Issuing the document 文件发放国家”，指护照发放国我们必须填&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>&nbsp;，填“China&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html\" target=\"_blank\">中国</a>”。<br>第三行依次是文件类型，现在应选“ID document”，第二项文件号码填护照号码，这最重要，查票时不一定看姓名和出生日期，但护照号码一定不能填错。最后第三项它自动会跳出来“Full”。<br>填好之后就是付款，用信用卡付款。付款&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64941.html\" target=\"_blank\">成功</a>&nbsp;他会出现PDF版的电子票，你保存到电脑打印出来即可<br><br>2.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/139973.html\" target=\"_blank\">马林</a>&nbsp;斯基剧院购票<br>先打开&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/139973.html\" target=\"_blank\">马林</a>&nbsp;斯基剧院官网：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mariinsky.ru/en/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mariinsky.ru/en/</a>&nbsp;<br></p><div id=\"_j_photo_444921653\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444921653.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AC/16/wKgEaVygyuGAcRKTAAFkdDfOWn056.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444921754\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444921754.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AC/2E/wKgEaVygyu6ACvChAAHg4rPtrMM41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444921844\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444921844.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AC/48/wKgEaVygyviAfkHIAAOpn9Hh6fg20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_444921949\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/444921949.html\"><img src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/AC/58/wKgEaVygywCAE1cNAAIBhNSpOH824.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a></div><p>回头登陆后就可以开始买票了，选择信用卡支付，最好选择VISA卡，银联是不能买的。</p><div><h2>摩尔曼斯克</h2></div><p>经历了两天的长途跋涉，终于到达了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;。&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;机场很小，下飞机瞬间感受到了&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10852.html\" target=\"_blank\">北极</a>的冰冷。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426934599\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934599.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s3/M00/45/6B/wKgIDVxe0QGAUlgKAAKiwruXXgg22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934596\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934596.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s3/M00/45/6A/wKgIDVxe0QCAG9sQAAH_epJRxd053.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_430006235\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006235.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/BA/wKgEaVxntDKAC_f1AA0SI20bjII30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/7915616.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克机场</a></div><p><br>这是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10852.html\" target=\"_blank\">北极</a>&nbsp;圈城市的早上10点，天还是黑的，打开导航去最北端的麦当劳吃早餐。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426916664\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426916664.html\"><img src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D3/D1/wKgBEFxexJeAa9syABFzVGdbLLk98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934967\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934967.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/B2/21/wKgED1xe0TiANUS0AAq-eybvIqs07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426916667\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426916667.html\"><img src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D3/D3/wKgBEFxexJqAcyWgAAl1h3lmYnE27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><p>初见，以为在&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10746.html\" target=\"_blank\">北海道</a>&nbsp;。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426934590\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934590.html\"><img src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s4/M00/CB/90/wKgIDlxe0QCAfKoGAA0KujNcco070.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><p>这里就是最北端的麦当劳，店里有自助点餐机，可以中文点餐。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_430006403\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006403.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/C5/wKgEaVxntDmAAFV5AAyGxHHTgOM27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/33175508.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>麦当劳</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426916668\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426916668.html\"><img src=\"http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D3/D5/wKgBEFxexJuAKhdYAAc2eFA0pto92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/33175508.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>麦当劳</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_430006386\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006386.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/C3/wKgEaVxntDeAbTRqAAy0XGSI-mE97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/33175508.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>麦当劳</a></div><p>吃的那独有的薯块</p><div id=\"_j_photo_430006394\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006394.html\"><img src=\"http://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/C3/wKgEaVxntDiAILzkABXm5ekYUg804.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/33175508.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>麦当劳</a></div><p>饱饱的早餐后去列宁号核动力水面舰船</p><div id=\"_j_photo_430006254\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006254.html\"><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/BF/wKgEaVxntDWAVNX8AAur9afQv7w45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934964\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934964.html\"><img src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D1/D2/wKgBZ1xe0TeAQ3dvAAkLdRMBiP458.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>摩尔曼斯克</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_430006261\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/430006261.html\"><img src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/CE/C0/wKgEaVxntDaAB55kAA-SxzhCeiI88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/7688484.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>列宁号核动力破冰船</a></div><p>列宁号<br>世界上第一艘核动力水面舰船，被称为“红色极地巨兽”<br><br></p><div><h2>捷里别尔卡</h2></div><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64656.html\" target=\"_blank\">摩尔曼斯克</a>&nbsp;一路向北<br>到达世界的最北端&nbsp;<img src=\"https://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/124.png\">&nbsp;捷里别尔卡<br>纪念与北冰洋的第一次邂逅<br>一个人走到世界尽头<br>看到了缤纷闪耀的舞动地&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10852.html\" target=\"_blank\">北极</a>&nbsp;光<br>在神秘的欧若拉女神的见证下<br>许下了2019的美好愿望</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426916677\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426916677.html\"><img src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/CB/9D/wKgBZ1xexY6AQFmWAAh7rTN1Aaw33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426934975\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934975.html\"><img src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D1/D2/wKgBZ1xe0TmAfyUxAAhulTLVxrI87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><p>这是用的打车软件打的车，小哥很好，所以就直接预约了第三天送我们去机场。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426934585\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426934585.html\"><img src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s4/M00/CB/90/wKgIDlxe0P-AcGiWAA4L0f005F068.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><p>一座荒废寂寥的村落，几只不肯离去的流浪狗<br>以为阳光沙滩才是绝配，阳光雪山沙滩更有一种雄劲霸气的美</p><div id=\"_j_photo_426929121\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426929121.html\"><img src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/AE/wKgBEFxezm6AcQi3AA8qmF0IH6w47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426929128\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426929128.html\"><img src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D8/B0/wKgBEFxeznCAAZs7ABCHW20mxlE87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/24798398.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>捷里别尔卡</a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_426916683\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10300/scenery_12376510/426916683.html\"><img src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s1/M00/A3/04/wKgIC1xexhmAW9RYAAVpeVJJVHg88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/34194748.html\" target=\"_blank\"><i></i>蒂瑞贝尔斯基海滩露营地餐厅</a></div>', '印象中的 ;俄罗斯 ;，世界上面积最大的国家，普金好帅， ;俄罗斯 ;人好美，就是这么肤浅的印象，哈哈哈en~~~其实并没有想法去踏足这个国家偶然间看到一篇旅行游记写 ;俄罗斯 ;看极光，被深深地吸引住了刚好 ;成都 ;往返 ;莫斯科 ;机票价格很美丽俄罗...', '2019-01-22 00:00:00', 12, 9000, 2, '潘大美女', '2019-05-06 20:15:43', '2019-05-06 20:15:43', '俄罗斯', '俄罗斯', 2, 5, 0);

